brokerageName: Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Starck Real Estate
description: Come and see our updated sophisticated new look. Welcome to 400 E. Randolph, Unit 1229 an outstanding truly move in two bedroom, two bath condo in one of Chicago's Premier Luxury Buildings with fantastic views from newer windows and private balcony. Entire Unit has been freshly painted and features Open concept perfect for todays modern living with updated kitchen and baths, newer stylish lighting fixtures, and true hardwood floors. Full amenity building offers resort lifestyle including glass domed indoor pool, sundeck, state of the air fitness center, racquet ball, pickleball & basketball courts, party room and much more. Prime location steps from Grant/Millenium/Maggie Daley Parks, Riverwalk, Lakefront and the loop. Additional perks include 24 hour security, shuttle bus service and assessments that include heat, a/c, gas and expanded cable. Great gem in the heart of downtown.
